**POE**

**What I changed**

Firstly, I added 4 more pages the Addpage.tsx ,Reservation.tsx ,Payment.tsx and App.js. I added pictures of all the dishes in the menu inside the assets file

Secondly, I changed the Desing of the picker of stater, main course, dessert in part2 it had not shape but was rather just a dropdown list picker and now it is placed inside a square shaped box whereby I can scroll through my option while the information remains in the box. Then I changed the way the information will be added in part2 when I pressed the add button the information would be displayed under the add button but now in the POE when I press the add button the information is placed in a different page/ next page.

Thirdly, I changed the way the design of the menu was. Previously in part2 I only had a pink themed menu and now it is grey. I added pictures in my menu as well. In part 2 I only had the number of dishes available in the menu but now in the POE I have the average price of the items in the menu and the average price of a course/per person. I removed the chef button. I added a select button so that user can select the dishes they plan to eat after reservations have been made and the user has the option to select more than one dish. I added a reserve button, this reserve button also has a counter that counts the number of dishes the user has selected, and the user will press the reserve button to make reservations, the reserve button will redirect the user to a reservation platform. I added a reservation platform where the user will select the Date, time and the amount of people they are making reservations for, with a submit button. I added a form where the user will press the submit button and will be redirected to form where the user adds their personal information such as Name, surname, phone number, email address after that I added a payment toll where the user will make a payment and personal card detail and will press the submit button to submit the reservation information. I added the average price of the course/dish per person, full price, the number of guests, time of reservation and all the user’s personal details.
